org.openbel.framework.common.xbel.parser
Class XBELConverter

java.lang.Object
  org.openbel.framework.common.xbel.parser.XBELConverter
All Implemented Interfaces:
XMLConverter<XBELDocument>
Direct Known Subclasses:
XBELValidatingConverter
public class XBELConverter
extends Object
implements XMLConverter<XBELDocument>

Implements an XML converter to convert from XML to XBELDocument objects. The JAXBContext is established on object construction, but creating the Marshaller and Unmarshaller is deferred until the marshal and unmarshal operations are called. This allows the Marshaller and Unmarshaller instances to be garbage collected when the operations complete.
